    options: ["Whether the employees have been with the company for more than 5 years","Whether compensating controls (e.g., management review of purchases, independent reconciliation) mitigate the risk to an acceptable level","Whether the company is publicly traded or private","Whether the affected account balance is above or below $100,000"],
