    educational: "Confirmation is a crucial audit procedure for verifying account balances directly with third parties. When management restricts this procedure, it creates a scope limitation. Auditors must assess the impact of this limitation on their ability to obtain sufficient appropriate audit evidence and, ultimately, on their opinion.",
