    examTip: "Remember that personal financial statements use current values, not historical costs, and focus on providing a snapshot of an individual's net worth.",
    memoryAid: "Think of 'Personal = Present' – Personal financial statements use PRESENT values.",
    reference: "ASC 274; AR-C §80",
