    examTip: "Remember the acronym 'OR FAM' (Objective, Responsibilities, Framework, Assurance, Management) to recall the key components of an audit engagement letter.",
    memoryAid: "OR FAM - Objective, Responsibilities, Framework, Assurance, Management",
