    examTip: "Always remember that communication with the predecessor auditor (with client permission) is a *mandatory* step before accepting a new audit engagement.",
    memoryAid: "Think 'Before Accept, Must Connect': Before accepting a new client, you MUST connect with the predecessor auditor.",
