    educational: "Restricted-use reports are crucial when the financial information is prepared using criteria only understood or relevant to specific users. This ensures that the report isn't misinterpreted or misapplied by parties lacking the necessary context. Understanding the intended audience is key to determining whether a report should be restricted.",
