      1: "Why option B is CORRECT - Management's integrity, ethical values, and tone at the top set the ethical standard for the entire organization. This 'tone' influences the control consciousness of its people and is the bedrock upon which all other internal control components are built.",
      2: "Why option C is WRONG - Accounting software is a tool used to implement controls, but it's not the foundation of the control environment. Its effectiveness depends on the ethical environment and how it's used.",
