      1: "Why option B is WRONG - Lack of independence requires a disclaimer of opinion, as the auditor cannot objectively form an opinion on the financial statements.",
      2: "Why option C is WRONG - A material and pervasive departure from GAAP requires an adverse opinion, indicating that the financial statements are not fairly presented.",
