    examTip: "Focus on the level of assurance provided by each type of engagement (audit vs. review vs. compilation) and the corresponding wording in the report.",
    memoryAid: "ARC: Audit - Reasonable assurance, Review - Limited assurance, Compilation - No assurance.",
    reference: "AR-C 90.35",
