    options: ["Immediately issue a qualified opinion due to the related party transaction.","Communicate the information to management and those charged with governance regarding the related party relationship and transaction.","Disregard the information, as the transaction occurred with an entity that is not directly related to Miller Manufacturing.","Expand the audit procedures to directly confirm the transaction details with Apex Distribution's bank."],
