    options: ["Obtain a written representation from management regarding their intent to execute the plan and believe it will alleviate the going concern issue.","Compare XYZ's expense reduction plan to industry benchmarks and evaluate the reasonableness of the assumptions underlying the plan.","Review XYZ's cash flow projections assuming the sale of the division and the full amount of the line of credit are realized.","Obtain a legal opinion on the enforceability of the sale agreement for the division and the line of credit agreement."],
