    options: ["Management acknowledges its responsibility for the fair presentation of inventory in accordance with the applicable financial reporting framework and confirms that adequate provisions for inventory obsolescence have been made and properly disclosed.","Management acknowledges its responsibility for the selection and application of accounting policies and confirms that the inventory obsolescence provision is consistent with industry standards.","Management acknowledges its responsibility for the design and implementation of internal control over financial reporting, including controls to prevent and detect material misstatements related to inventory obsolescence.","Management acknowledges that the auditor, Sarah Chen, is responsible for determining the adequacy of the inventory obsolescence provision."],
