    options: ["Increase the sample size of sales invoices tested to confirm the initial assessment of control risk.","Conclude that the controls are operating effectively because the deviation rate is below 10%.","Consider the implications of the control deficiency on other related financial statement assertions.","Reduce the scope of substantive procedures since the initial assessment of control risk was low."],
