    options: ["Accept the engagement without further consideration, as no formal charges were filed against the CEO.","Accept the engagement but only after obtaining a waiver of liability from ZZZ Corp's board of directors regarding the CEO's past actions.","Decline the engagement unless ZZZ Corp's audit committee conducts an independent investigation into the CEO's past actions and provides satisfactory assurances.","Decline the engagement unless ZZZ Corp.'s prior auditor provides a written statement attesting to the CEO's integrity."],
