    examTip: "Focus on identifying factors that directly impact the firm's ability to perform a quality audit. Competence, objectivity, and resources are key considerations.",
    memoryAid: "CRO - Competence, Resources, Objectivity - Remember to consider these three elements when accepting or continuing an audit engagement.",
