    options: ["A. Immediately report the deficiency to the AICPA Professional Ethics Division and the applicable state board of accountancy.","B. Design and implement a remediation plan to address the deficiency as soon as possible, and evaluate the effect of the deficiency to determine if it is pervasive.","C. Immediately withdraw from all existing engagements with clients in the cannabis industry to mitigate any potential harm.","D. Document the deficiency and include it in the firm's next peer review submission for review and evaluation."],
