    options: ["The aggressive revenue recognition practices, coupled with the compensation structure and complex new accounting standard.","The significant related party transactions, as they inherently involve management override of controls.","The data migration issues with the new ERP system, as they could affect the reliability of financial reporting data.","All of the identified risks should be considered equally significant and require the same level of audit attention."],
