    question: "Your audit client, Apex Manufacturing, has a large number of relatively small accounts receivable balances. After assessing inherent and control risk as low for accounts receivable, you are considering the use of negative confirmation requests. Which of the following conditions would be least likely to support the use of negative confirmations for Apex's accounts receivable?",
