    options: ["Sell her husband's stock in ABC Company or remove herself from the audit engagement.","Disclose the ownership to ABC Company's management but continue with the audit, documenting the potential conflict of interest.","Disclose the ownership to the audit committee and if they approve, continue with the audit, documenting the potential conflict of interest.","Engage another CPA firm to perform a concurring peer review of her work on the ABC Company audit."],
