    question: "Apex CPAs, a firm with 15 professionals, recently implemented its system of quality management (SQM) designed in accordance with SQMS 1. As part of the monitoring activities, the firm's quality control director identified a significant deficiency in the firm's engagement performance process on a recent audit engagement. Which of the following actions would be MOST appropriate for Apex CPAs to take FIRST regarding this deficiency?",
