    examTip: "Focus on determining whether the subsequent event provides evidence about conditions that existed at year-end. If it does, adjustment is required. Always consider disclosure requirements in addition to adjustment requirements.",
    memoryAid: "Think of 'Adjust' for events 'Already' present at year end",
    reference: "AU-C 560",
