    options: ["Confirm the transaction price and terms directly with Zenith LLC's management and review supporting documentation held by Zenith LLC.","Obtain a written representation from management stating that all related party transactions have been properly identified and disclosed.","Review Nexus Corp.'s legal counsel's assessment of the transaction's compliance with applicable laws and regulations.","Issue a qualified opinion on Nexus Corp.'s financial statements due to the potential material misstatement."],
