    options: ["Send a second confirmation request to Ross Company and if they do not respond, assume the balance is correct.","Examine shipping documents and sales invoices for transactions between Miller Manufacturing and Ross Company around December 31, 2023.","Increase the sample size of accounts receivable confirmations to compensate for the non-response from Ross Company.","Automatically classify the $75,000 balance as a material misstatement and require Miller Manufacturing to write it off."],
