    options: ["Perform a trend analysis of selling, general, and administrative expenses to determine if there were significant decreases that could explain the higher gross profit.","Compare Zenith's gross profit margin to industry averages and investigate any significant differences.","Obtain production records and perform a detailed analysis of direct material and direct labor costs, focusing on quantity and price variances.","Review sales contracts to identify any unusual terms or conditions that could have artificially inflated revenues."],
