    options: ["Confirming the inventory balance with the warehouse custodian and relying solely on that confirmation as sufficient appropriate audit evidence.","Performing test counts of inventory items at the warehouse in conjunction with obtaining a direct confirmation from the warehouse custodian and evaluating the warehouse's internal controls.","Physically observing the inventory at the warehouse at the balance sheet date and tracing a sample of items to the client's perpetual inventory records.","Reviewing the client's shipping and receiving records for the period immediately before and after year-end to identify any unusual transactions."],
