    options: ["Compare the current year's depreciation expense to the prior year's depreciation expense, adjusted for the change in asset base due to normal capital expenditures.","Calculate the ratio of cost of goods sold to sales and compare it to the prior year and industry averages, considering the change in inventory valuation method.","Compare the current year's selling, general, and administrative expenses to the prior year's expenses, adjusted for inflation.","Calculate the ratio of current assets to current liabilities and compare it to the prior year and industry averages."],
