      2: "Selecting only the top 50 accounts may not provide sufficient coverage of the larger accounts that constitute 75% of the total balance, potentially missing significant misstatements.",
      3: "Selecting accounts based on credit ratings is not directly related to the risk of material misstatement due to aggressive sales targets. The focus should be on account balances, not creditworthiness.",
