    question: "ABC Company's year-end is December 31, 2023, and the auditor is completing the audit on March 10, 2024. On February 20, 2024, a fire completely destroyed one of ABC's major warehouses, resulting in a material loss of inventory. ABC Company's financial statements do not reflect this loss. Which of the following actions should the auditor take FIRST?",
