    options: ["Increase the assessed level of inherent risk related to inventory valuation and consider performing additional procedures to evaluate the recoverability of Apex's investment in titanium alloy X42.","Disclose the potential bankruptcy of Titan Alloys Inc. in the auditor's report as a going concern matter, regardless of Apex's current financial position.","Reduce the scope of testing on inventory because Apex has a 6-month supply on hand, mitigating the immediate risk.","Rely solely on management's representations regarding the availability of alternative suppliers and the impact on Apex's production schedule."],
