    options: ["A. Increase the sample size for testing the operating effectiveness of controls over the reconciliation of bank statements.","B. Perform analytical procedures on revenue accounts throughout the year and investigate any unexpected fluctuations, focusing on trends and ratios.","C. Select a sample of sales invoices recorded near the end of the reporting period and examine supporting documentation for evidence of shipment and customer acceptance.","D. Evaluate the design effectiveness of the IT general controls related to user access and change management for the company's accounting system."],
