    options: ["Ignore the deficiency, as it only occurred in a small sample of engagements and the firm has limited resources.","Accept the deficiency and document it in the firm's internal control documentation.","Design and implement a remediation plan to address the deficiency, which includes determining the root cause, evaluating the severity and pervasiveness of the deficiency, and determining whether further action is necessary for the specific engagement.","Report the deficiency to the AICPA as a potential violation of professional standards."],
    correctAnswer: 2,
