    examTip: "Pay close attention to who owns the stock and their relationship to the covered member. Direct ownership by a covered member or their immediate family generally impairs independence.",
    memoryAid: "D-I-S-C: Direct financial interest, Indirect financial interest, Service as officer/director, Close family member employment often impair independence.",
    reference: "AICPA Code of Professional Conduct, ET 1.220.010",
