    options: ["Smith & Jones' independence is impaired because performing bookkeeping services for a public company audit client is always prohibited.","Smith & Jones' independence is not impaired as long as Apex management oversees the bookkeeping services, reviews the work performed, and accepts responsibility for the financial statements.","Smith & Jones' independence is impaired only if the fees for the bookkeeping services are expected to exceed the audit fees.","Smith & Jones' independence is not impaired if the bookkeeping services are routine and mechanical in nature."],
