    options: ["ABC Company’s management is responsible for overseeing the bookkeeping services and makes all significant judgments related to the financial statements.","Smith & Jones has assigned a separate team of professionals to perform the bookkeeping services, distinct from the audit team.","The fees for the bookkeeping services are based on a fixed fee arrangement, unrelated to the audit fee.","Smith & Jones prepared the original source documents, such as sales invoices, for ABC Company."],
